    <p>Unlike existing factor analysis techniques for multi data, UNMF takes in tidy data [<xref rid="ref5" ref-type="bibr">5</xref>, <xref rid="ref9" ref-type="bibr">9</xref>] as input, which is a data format that is coherent in structure and meaning and satisfies the following conditions:</p>
