  <sec id="sec6">
    <title>Default prior distribution</title>
    <p>We set the gamma prior distribution weakly informative [<xref rid="ref20" ref-type="bibr">20</xref>] as not to rule out the information contained in data. This means, even if the observation has many 0s or outlier, numerical errors are not occurred, and otherwise provide similar result to the maximum likelihood estimator.</p>
